class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1418ac192fdd5864084dce0b355735c0cfc063","tid":630843,"uid":65984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:43:41.000Z","msg":"國策日日變, 邊個敢投資<br />\n<br />\n依家叫你比錢起, 唔知幾時叫停就血本無歸<br />\n<br />\n海南唔係未試過, 早幾年都話過支持發展成賭城, 點知一叫停就要變私人會所, 仲要唔比金錢交易, 笑死人"},{"pid":"8a1713987bfe4b4d1242a9f36a29873736b99cbd","tid":630843,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"狗會係從化個狗場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}